    public interface BlackBoxOracle<A extends net.automatalib.automaton.concept.Output<I,​D>,​I,​D>
extends InclusionOracle<A,​I,​D>
    Decides whether some words that do not satisfy properties evaluated by getPropertyOracles() on a given hypothesis, are included in a language. If there is such a word not included, it serves as a counter example for the given hypothesis.
